HEADWORD: Actinometry
<hw>Ac`ti*nom"e*try</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The measurement of the force of solar radiation.</def>
<rj><au>Maury.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The measurement of the chemical or actinic energy of
light.</def> <rj><au>Abney.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Actinomycetales</ent>⟦br⟧
